{[#] This version of isolated queen's pawn (pawn structure #5) is another
common pawn structure in the Ragozin. It is clearly in Black's favor to get
this kind of pawn structure because the isolated pawn on d5 is offset by the
one on c3. In fact, it is often more difficult to protect the c3-pawn than the
d5- one. The most common transformation of the pawn structure is, obviously,
into pawn structure #6.}  *

