23. Nh8+ (23. Nxe7 Qxe5 $1) 23... Ke8 24. Qh5+ Kd7 25. Rxd4+ Kc6 $19) 21...
Kxf7 22. Qxf3 Kg8 23. Qg4+ Kh7 24. Nxe6 Nxe6 25. Qxe6 Bf8 26. Rac1 Kh8 $17) (
13. Ng3 {might be a tad premature due to Black's unexpected resource:} b5 $1
$146 {[#] This is an original way to quickly develop the bishop to the h1-a8
