17. Bxh3 h5 18. Bxf5 Qxf5 19. Nf3 $13) 15... Bd6 $1 16. g3 (16. Rxb7 Bxf4 17.
exf4 O-O $13) 16... Bxf4 17. gxf4 Bxb1 18. Qxb1 Qd6 19. Bxh3 $44 {0-1 (95)
Svane,R (2542)-Socko,B (2617) Dresden GER 2016}) 9... Nxg3 10. hxg3 Nxd4 11. e3
Bxc3 {White has tried both captures in practice:} 12. bxc3 ({After} 12. Rxc3
Ne6 13. Nf3 c6 14. Rh6 $44 {White surely has compensation for the pawn and the
