Nd6 $11 {0-1 (83) Wang Doudou (2234)-Tan Zhongyi (2518) Xinghua CHN 2016})
12... Re8 13. Rc1 c6 14. Bd3 Bxd3 15. Qxd3 a5 $11 {In an equal and quiet
