Qxe6 24. Qxe6+ Rxe6 $11 {and it peters out to a draw.}) ({A Catalan hybrid} 6.
g3 {[#] has been played from time to time. It is not an ambitious setup - it
just leads to a regular middlegame with mutual chances.} Be7 {I have a slight
preference for this move over 6...Bd6, although that one should be fine, as
