chances.} 9. Bf4 {This is the main move.} ({The alternatives met in practice
are:} 9. Ne5 Nbd7 10. Nd3 a5 11. Bf4 Re8 12. Rc1 Nf8 13. a3 Ne6 14. Be5 Ng4 {
Black managed to win the bishop pair without allowing any weaknesses, for what
