10. Qb3 {This is the critical reply.} ({In the game, I played the uninspired:} 
10. Bd3 Bxd3 11. Qxd3 Be7 12. O-O O-O $11 {1/2-1/2 (57) Kuljasevic, D (2538)
-Saric,I (2677) Pozega CRO 2018}) 10... Nb6 {Black defends both his hanging
